ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS by repealing paragraph 159.6(c) to protect the integrity of the refugee status determination system by ensuring that refugee protection claimants who have had the opportunity to have their claims assessed in the U.S. are not coming to Canada to make these claims.
